N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5410.1 - Duty to update address

State Regulations
A commission licensee or applicant for a license has a
continuing duty to inform the commission of any change of address, including a
change in an electronic mail address (if such person or entity provides an
electronic mail address to the commission), in connection with an application
or otherwise. Notes
